 },
 {
  "i": 3,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Delirious with fever, let's take the helm"
 },
 {
  "i": 4,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Even an old treasure map covered in dust..."
 },
 {
  "i": 5,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Isn't a legend if it's been proved real!"
 },
 {
  "i": 6,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "For our own storms, all we have to do is"
 },
 {
  "i": 7,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "Ride someone else's biorythm..."
 },
 {
  "i": 8,
  "style": "Lyrics",
  "name": "",
  "text": "And pretend that it isn't there!"
 },
 {
  "i": 9,
  "style": "Lyrics",
